  <brief_title>Standard Versus Advanced Antimicrobial Dressing Containing Ionic Silver Following Colorectal Cancer Surgery</brief_title>
  <acronym>AM</acronym>
  <official_title>Surgical Sites Infections Following Colorectal Cancer Surgery. A Randomized Prospective Trial Comparing Standard and Advanced Antimicrobial Dressing Containing Ionic Silver.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
