  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the efficacy of treatment with hydrofibre dressing
      in comparison with the efficacy of standard dressing in terms of prevalence of surgical site
      infections (SSI) in patients who underwent colorectal resection for malignancy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
